  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You adjust the location of an ally to a better tactical position. You move one willing creature within range 5 feet. This movement does not provoke opportunity attacks. The creature moves bodily through the intervening space (as opposed to teleporting), so there can be no physical obstacle (such as a wall or a door) in the path.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target an additional willing creature for each slot level above 1st.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
